flowRoot.flowPara: The dialer page of the phone app.

When the user types the numbers, relevant contacts appear above. These relevant contacts can be either contacts that their phone number contains the numbers typed, or contacts that their name starts with the corresponding letters (for example 6453 should show all the Mikes in contacts as well as any phone numbers that start with, or contain 6453)
Number 4 is showing the pressed state of the number
Text for the number to be called
The keypad is visually centered, not mathematically. If we mathematically center either the numbers or the full keypad it looks wrong.
